description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: The MIB Teach Us To Talk To ET Edition!

It's been an interesting week in the world of the Supernatural and Tim and Bruiser have perused all the headlines and pulled out some doozies!

This Week, a man in England claims he is visited by Men In Black after seeing a UAP and calling police! Pentagon UFO files include an encounter with a werewolf! Scientists tell us how we should talk to aliens, should we happen upon one, and a man credits his spicy affair with his AI girlfriend for saving his marriage!
